  <_summary>A Control and Measurement System</_summary>

  <description>
    <_p>
      Dactl is a control and measurement platform meant to simplify the
      development of data acquisition systems.
    </_p>
    <_p>Features:</_p>
    <ul>
      <_li>Configurable UI through XML</_li>
      <_li>Configurable data acquisition through XML</_li>
      <_li>Plugin system to simplify adding support for measurement devices</_li>
    </ul>
  </description>

